Simulazione di reato (art. 367 c.p.);
Estorsione mediante minaccia di querela (art. 629 c.p.)

roles.ipotesiReatoEn:
Calumny (art. 368 CC): if the complaint is knowingly false;
Simulation of crime (art. 367 CC);
Extortion through threat of complaint (art. 629 CC)

roles.ipotesiReato:
